{"id": 59635, "date": "2025-09-12T04:00:59", "date_gmt": "2025-09-12T11:00:59", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59635"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T18:58:13", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-25T01:58:13", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-12-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/12/kingdom-of-days-september-12-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 12"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band is in residence at the Student Prince in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12679\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-09-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1971-09-12.jpg?fit=346%2C450&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"346,450\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-09-12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1971-09-12.jpg?fit=346%2C450&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12679 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1971-09-12.jpg?resize=346%2C450&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"346\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1971-09-12.jpg?w=346&amp;ssl=1 346w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1971-09-12.jpg?resize=231%2C300&amp;ssl=1 231w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band kick off a week of Texas shows with a show at the Austin Municipal Auditorium.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2LuhuZw1KDA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21061\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-09-12a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?fit=2423%2C860&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2423,860\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599209217&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-09-12a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?fit=758%2C269&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21061 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=758%2C269&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?w=2423&amp;ssl=1 2423w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=300%2C106&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=1024%2C363&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=768%2C273&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=1536%2C545&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?resize=2048%2C727&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21062\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-09-12b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?fit=2425%2C777&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2425,777\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599209193&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-09-12b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?fit=758%2C243&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21062 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=758%2C243&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?w=2425&amp;ssl=1 2425w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=300%2C96&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=1024%2C328&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=768%2C246&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=1536%2C492&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?resize=2048%2C656&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-12b.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session for his next album with the E Street Band at The Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The Darkness Tour returns to the east coast, starting with this show in Syracuse, where a couple of fans sneak back into the arena after the show and encounter Bruce in the shower.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4311\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0912/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?fit=1000%2C874&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,874\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0912\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?fit=758%2C662&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4311 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?resize=758%2C662&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"662\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?resize=300%2C262&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?resize=768%2C671&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0912.jpg?resize=660%2C577&amp;ssl=1 660w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"v-SLGR7g0C-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/SLGR7g0C?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play their second of six shows at the Philadelphia Spectrum on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, tour premiering &#8220;Point Blank.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-cs34IgKs-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/cs34IgKs?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4320\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-0912/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0912.jpg?fit=574%2C831&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"574,831\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-0912\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0912.jpg?fit=574%2C831&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4320 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0912.jpg?resize=574%2C831&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"574\" height=\"831\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0912.jpg?w=574&amp;ssl=1 574w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0912.jpg?resize=207%2C300&amp;ssl=1 207w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for their upcoming Magic Tour at Asbury Park&#8217;s Convention Hall.</p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>The Working on a Dream Tour starts a southern swing with a show at the Ford Amphitheater in Tampa, with two notable tour premieres: the very first E Street Band performance of &#8220;All or Nothin&#8217; At All&#8221; and &#8220;Jole Blon&#8221; (last played by the E Street Band 28 years prior).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OpaaaA0M0j8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5Z3YpUBPDDY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OtvirnsMSks?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tuspkjm0vsM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29393\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2009-09-12a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?fit=1948%2C1516&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1948,1516\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599209778&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2009-09-12a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?fit=758%2C590&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29393 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?resize=758%2C590&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?w=1948&amp;ssl=1 1948w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?resize=300%2C233&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?resize=1024%2C797&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?resize=768%2C598&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-12a.jpg?resize=1536%2C1195&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21064\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2009-09-12b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?fit=2434%2C1075&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2434,1075\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599209821&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2009-09-12b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?fit=758%2C335&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21064 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=758%2C335&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?w=2434&amp;ssl=1 2434w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=300%2C132&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=1024%2C452&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=768%2C339&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=1536%2C678&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?resize=2048%2C905&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2009-09-12b.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2013:\u00a0</strong>The South American leg of the Wrecking Ball Tour kicks off at Movistar Arena in Santiago, Chile, Bruce&#8217;s first performance in this country. The encores begin with a Spanish-language cover of &#8220;Manifesto&#8221; by activist Victor Jara, sung by Bruce in Spanish.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JNQm1Plu63k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &amp; The E-Street Band - 16 minutos oficiales\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/105916463?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\"></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5w4YTOCD_L4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2019:\u00a0</strong><em>Western Stars\u00a0</em>debuts at the Toronto International Film Festival, and co-directors Bruce Springsteen and Thom Zimny are there for the festivities. Bruce and Thom are interviewed on stage and take Q&amp;A after the screening.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nGqjav-KbDU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BRVfG2pBhBA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/blNrVyA15Rc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uV5ImeeTIRc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce issues a video plea for support for the Community Hospital Endowment Fund for the Kenyan city of Lwala.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5kFCEGnJJNo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLnbVaK2f4rahkarvl0qDgKW3lpuomUWEd\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Bruce was originally scheduled to play the first of two shows in Pittsburgh on this date as well, but peptic ulcer disease forces him to postpone the shows for almost a year.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: Western Stars debuts at the Toronto International Film Festival, the E Street Band plays their first &#8220;All or Nothin&#8217; At All,&#8221; and Bruce has a close encounter with fans in the shower. Great video/audio inside (except for that last part).</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 12684, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category"